BerkeleyLogo is a free Logo interpreter written by BrianHarvey and others at the University of California at Berkeley.  The C source code is available in a tarball, but ported binaries for Mac OS X and Windows are also available.

* http://www.cs.berkeley.edu/~bh/logo.html

